recitals:
,
Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community,
Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 2908/83 of 4 October 1983 introducing a common measure for the restructuring, modernization and development of fisheries and the development of aquaculture (1), and in particular Article 12 (4) thereof,
Whereas applications for aid under the common measure provided for in Regulation (EEC) No 2908/83 contain all the information enabling the projects to be examined by reference to the criteria set out therein;
Whereas, in order to facilitate both rapid examination and comparison of applications, the information must be presented in identical form in each application;
Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Standing Committee for the Fishing Industry,
